-- North Sea Statfjord Crude Oil Loadings to Drop in August
-- B y   L a u r a   H u r s t
-- 2013-07-05T11:58:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-05/north-sea-statfjord-crude-oil-loadings-to-drop-in-august-1-.html
North Sea Statfjord crude exports are
scheduled to fall to four cargoes in August, down from six
cargoes in July, according to a loading program obtained by
 Bloomberg News .  Exports will total 3.255 million barrels next month, or
105,000 barrels a day, compared with 158,387 barrels a day this
month. August shipments will comprise three lots of 800,000
barrels and another cargo of 855,000 barrels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Laura Hurst in London at 
 lhurst3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  